dise.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Nasa\u0304'i\u0304 674 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":38247,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2022\/09\/13\/tawakkul-excess\/","url_meta":{"origin":37898,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Tawakkul: Trust in Allah, but do not store to excess","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 13, 2022","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, entered the room of Bilal and he found a pile of dates with him. The Prophet said, \u201cWhat is this, O Bilal?\u201d Bilal said, \u201cThey are dates I have stored for you.\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cWoe to\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":33062,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/08\/03\/how-bilal-got-into-jannah\/","url_meta":{"origin":37898,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Sahaba: How Bilal ibn Rabah got into Paradise","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 3, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said to Bilal at the time of dawn prayer, \u201cO Bilal, tell me of the most hopeful deed you practiced in Islam.\u00a0 I heard the scuffle of your sandals before me in Paradise.\u201d Bilal said, \u201cThe most hopeful deed\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Rig